# onboard.tape — vhs script for the onboard demo GIF.

Output "demos/onboard.gif"

Set Theme "GitHub Dark"
Set FontFamily "JetBrains Mono"
Set FontSize 14
Set Width 1080
Set Height 920
Set Padding 24
Set PlaybackSpeed 1.0
Set Framerate 24

Hide
Type "clear && bash demos/scenario-onboard.sh"
Enter
Show

Sleep 16s
